metadata.name: Grieving
metadata.description:
This is very unique images.i used my daughters PE clothes and my wide pants which i wont wear anymore. i just cut those and put on her head (no sewing too) . i have behind scene photo on my Instagram.

i wanted to create theme of *grieve* because me and my kids were having hard time last year. suddenly their father left us and she still having hard time. also we are all sad about covid changed our life too. so many meanings has this images for me and my daughter.
